@struct ConfirmationGate version:1 format:toon
@struct
  description: Zero-trust confirmation gate policy — no action executes without user approval
  mode: all

@struct SafetyGates
  description: Four-level safety gate chain for execution
  rules:
    - Gate 1 [DestructiveCheck]: 掃描命令是否包含 rm -rf、format、del、Remove-Item 等破壞性操作
    - Gate 2 [PathScopeVerification]: 全域模式下必須驗證執行路徑在允許列表中
    - Gate 3 [SubagentAudit]: 審查 17 代理人分工是否正確路由
    - Gate 4 [ExecutionLog]: 記錄所有已批准/拒絕的動作於 Audit Log

@struct AllowedPaths
  description: Allowed execution path roots for global mode
  paths:
    - C:\Users\MasterYee\Documents\Program
    - C:\Users\MasterYee\Documents
    - C:\Users\MasterYee
    - C:\Program Files
    - C:\ProgramData
  blocked_patterns:
    - C:\Windows
    - C:\System32
    - C:\Program Files (x86)\Windows

@struct RiskLevels
  description: Action risk classification for approval prioritization
  Low:
    description: 讀取文件、列出目錄、搜索文件
    auto_approve: false
  Medium:
    description: 修改現有文件、創建新文件、重命名
    auto_approve: false
  High:
    description: 編譯 Rust 專案、執行測試、修改系統配置
    auto_approve: false
  Critical:
    description: 刪除文件/目錄、執行 rm -rf、格式化、修改 .gitignore
    auto_approve: false

@struct Workflow
  description: Confirmation gate workflow — sequential execution chain
  steps:
    - Step 1: Orchestrator 產生 PendingAction 列表
    - Step 2: PendingActions 以 ConfirmationGate UI 展示於右側面板
    - Step 3: 使用者逐項 Approve / Reject
    - Step 4: 僅 Approve 的動作進入沙盒執行
    - Step 5: SandboxRuntimeTester 回傳 Exit Code + Stderr
    - Step 6: 執行結果記錄於 Audit Log
    - Step 7: 若 Exit Code != 0，自動觸發 Delta-Only 自愈重寫

@struct LocaleSafety
  description: Locale calibration must happen before any Shell execution
  rules:
    - Windows: 注入 chcp 65001 切換至 UTF-8
    - Linux/macOS: 設置 LANG=zh_TW.UTF-8 與 LC_ALL=zh_TW.UTF-8
    - 所有命令執行前必須校準語系
    - 禁止無校準直接調用 Shell

@end
